  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8 \u0dad\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0db6\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dd3",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The fuel queue takes another toll",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Borella police say that a person who was waiting in line at the IOC petrol station on Borella Tikal Road has died in his luxury car.",
        "Sujeewa Vikum Gunaratne (60) of Hewagama Dissanayake, who was a resident of Angoda Gothatuwa, has died.",
        "Borella Police Station Chief Inspector AJMR Samarasinghe said that information has been received that the deceased person came by car to get fuel on the 4th of the previous night.",
        "The body of the deceased has been deposited at the mortuary of the Colombo National Hospital for post-mortem examination.",
        "Investigations are being conducted on the instructions of Borella Police Station Chief Inspector AJMR Samarasinghe."
      ],
